    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-10 mb-4">Summary</h2>
    <p>High gas fees are growing pains for Ethereum. For small users, <strong>using Layer2 directly</strong> is the most practical solution; for large users, choosing off-peak hours + batch operations can significantly reduce costs.</p>
    <p class="mt-3">Long-term, Ethereum will evolve toward sharding and more efficient Rollup solutions — gas fee issues will gradually ease. But short-term, Layer2 is your best friend.</p>
